:1668134104,"deleted":0,"content":"老哥们，最近面临一个艰难的选择，目前工作在一家中厂，业绩挺不错，大概率 5 年内不裁员吧，之前也没裁员过。目前在成都税后大概总包有 27 万的样子。工作没啥压力，氛围也不错，同事关系很好，不咋加班，工作轻松，魔域时间多，6 点下班。感觉挺好的。\r\n\r\n但是最近又有一个新机会，就是去 211 大学（硕士母校）里面的技术岗，第一年 10 万，第二三年 15 万的样子。钱有点少，7 年不涨薪的样子，好处是有寒暑假， 早 10 晚 5 不加班，很好耍，几乎不干活。直接养老躺平。\r\n\r\n目前谈了个女朋友，主城区公务员，感情挺好的，她倾向于我在外面，反正也不怕失业，有她兜底。\r\n\r\n我自己的话，挺喜欢计算机的吧，能力感觉也还行，比较上进爱学习。\r\n\r\n目前就很纠结啊，到底是去学校还是安心公司呆着。\r\n\r\n请各位老哥给点意见。","content_rendered":"<p>老哥们，最近面临一个艰难的选择，目前工作在一家中厂，业绩挺不错，大概率 5 年内不裁员吧，之前也没裁员过。目前在成都税后大概总包有 27 万的样子。工作没啥压力，氛围也不错，同事关系很好，不咋加班，工作轻松，魔域时间多，6 点下班。感觉挺好的。</p>\n<p>但是最近又有一个新机会，就是去 211 大学（硕士母校）里面的技术岗，第一年 10 万，第二三年 15 万的样子。钱有点少，7 年不涨薪的样子，好处是有寒暑假， 早 10 晚 5 不加班，很好耍，几乎不干活。直接养老躺平。</p>\n<p>目前谈了个女朋友，主城区公务员，感情挺好的，她倾向于我在外面，反正也不怕失业，有她兜底。</p>\n<p>我自己的话，挺喜欢计算机的吧，能力感觉也还行，比较上进爱学习。</p>\n<p>目前就很纠结啊，到底是去学校还是安心公司呆着。</p>\n<p>请各位老哥给点意见。</p>\n","last_modified":1668134104,"replies":21,"id":894390},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965","name":"android","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965","title":"Android","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","topics":9837,"footer":"","header":"来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。","title_alternative":"Android","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","stars":5192,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":39,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":426922,"username":"ZhiyuanLin","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ZhiyuanLin","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/46c5/02bf/426922_mini.png?m=1570871118","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/46c5/02bf/426922_normal.png?m=1570871118","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/46c5/02bf/426922_large.png?m=1570871118","created":1562248667,"last_modified":1570871118},"last_reply_by":"wanqiuyao","last_touched":1668145219,"title":"严重安全漏洞：安全补丁早于 2022 年 11 月的 Android 设备可能存在通用的免密解锁 Bug","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894437","created":1668140305,"deleted":0,"content":"https://bugs.xdavidhu.me/google/2022/11/10/accidental-70k-google-pixel-lock-screen-bypass/\r\nhttps://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=33544883\r\nhttps://github.com/aosp-mirror/platform_frameworks_base/commit/ecbed81c3a331f2f0458923cc7e744c85ece96da\r\n\r\n所需工具：启用 PIN Lock 的 SIM 卡（需要知道 PUK ）\r\n复现方法：\r\n1. 插入 SIM 卡并重启\r\n2. 故意输错 3 次 PIN 导致 SIM 卡被锁定\r\n3. 输入 PUK 解锁被锁定的 SIM 卡并重置 PIN ，会发现 SIM 卡锁和锁屏同时被解除了。\r\n\r\n漏洞原因：\r\nAndroid SIM 锁和普通锁屏使用同一个 class ，解锁成功时.dismiss()会被调用，用于消除锁屏 UI 。\r\n解锁 PUK 时.dismiss()被错误用在所有当前锁屏 UI 上了。\r\n\r\n2022-10 补丁和更早的的 Pixel 全系可复现，2022-11 补丁修复。\r\n漏洞在 AOSP 上，理论上影响所有厂商的 Android 手机。","content_rendered":"<p><a href=\"https://bugs.xdavidhu.me/google/2022/11/10/accidental-70k-google-pixel-lock-screen-bypass/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://bugs.xdavidhu.me/google/2022/11/10/accidental-70k-google-pixel-lock-screen-bypass/</a>\n<a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=33544883\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=33544883</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/aosp-mirror/platform_frameworks_base/commit/ecbed81c3a331f2f0458923cc7e744c85ece96da\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/aosp-mirror/platform_frameworks_base/commit/ecbed81c3a331f2f0458923cc7e744c85ece96da</a></p>\n<p>所需工具：启用 PIN Lock 的 SIM 卡（需要知道 PUK ）\n复现方法：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>插入 SIM 卡并重启</li>\n<li>故意输错 3 次 PIN 导致 SIM 卡被锁定</li>\n<li>输入 PUK 解锁被锁定的 SIM 卡并重置 PIN ，会发现 SIM 卡锁和锁屏同时被解除了。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>漏洞原因：\nAndroid SIM 锁和普通锁屏使用同一个 class ，解锁成功时.dismiss()会被调用，用于消除锁屏 UI 。\n解锁 PUK 时.dismiss()被错误用在所有当前锁屏 UI 上了。</p>\n<p>2022-10 补丁和更早的的 Pixel 全系可复现，2022-11 补丁修复。\n漏洞在 AOSP 上，理论上影响所有厂商的 Android 手机。</p>\n","last_modified":1668140305,"replies":18,"id":894437},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1641783557","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1641783557","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2987,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557","stars":977,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":586293,"username":"Crackers","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Crackers","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5047984a67bfade6f9f9290911b52334?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5047984a67bfade6f9f9290911b52334?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5047984a67bfade6f9f9290911b52334?s=73&d=retro","created":1656481381,"last_modified":1656481381},"last_reply_by":"cnbatch","last_touched":1668147562,"title":"Window 计算器疑惑","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894432","created":1668139302,"deleted":0,"content":"是不是我脑子出了点问题＞﹏＜，还是昨天晚上没睡醒＞︿＜（昨天晚上确实是三点钟之后上床睡觉的，7.20 就起床了，吨吨吨）？\r\n\r\n1-(2+3)-(-4)*(-5)/(+6) 不应该等于 -7.3333...吗？\r\n咋计算器算的 6 ？(⊙ˍ⊙)？\r\n怎么得也是个负数吧...(￣︿￣)\r\n\r\n[![zCkKLd.png]( https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/11/11/zCkKLd.png)]( https://imgse.com/i/zCkKLd)","content_rendered":"<p>是不是我脑子出了点问题＞﹏＜，还是昨天晚上没睡醒＞︿＜（昨天晚上确实是三点钟之后上床睡觉的，7.20 就起床了，吨吨吨）？</p>\n<p>1-(2+3)-(-4)*(-5)/(+6) 不应该等于 -7.3333...吗？\n咋计算器算的 6 ？(⊙ˍ⊙)？\n怎么得也是个负数吧...(￣︿￣)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgse.com/i/zCkKLd\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"zCkKLd.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/11/11/zCkKLd.png\"/></a></p>\n","last_modified":1668139302,"replies":18,"id":894432},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1659331259","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1659331259","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":51874,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alt