st_modified":1407907197},"last_reply_by":"zliea","last_touched":1668131124,"title":"想买个显示器写代码看文档用，大家有啥好推荐吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894342","created":1668129469,"deleted":0,"content":"","content_rendered":"","last_modified":1668129469,"replies":15,"id":894342},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":192787,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3610,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":360458,"username":"qqqqqcy","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/qqqqqcy","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1b0d/f4c9/360458_mini.png?m=1663728040","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1b0d/f4c9/360458_normal.png?m=1663728040","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1b0d/f4c9/360458_large.png?m=1663728040","created":1541145318,"last_modified":1663728040},"last_reply_by":"wwwaaa","last_touched":1668140901,"title":"炒股怎么入门？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/894399","created":1668134959,"deleted":0,"content":"先不论炒股的必要性或者学不会不如不炒\r\n\r\n尝试看了一些相关的书，也断断续续实盘操作了一两年，收益理所当然是负的\r\n\r\n其实收益正负也倒还好，关键是感觉水平完全没提升，不像自己写代码或者学技术，明显的知道路线规划和学到什么程度了可以做出什么样的东西\r\n\r\n所以想问问大家，如果想炒股有这种掌控感、自信，应该是怎么一个学习路线呢","content_rendered":"<p>先不论炒股的必要性或者学不会不如不炒</p>\n<p>尝试看了一些相关的书，也断断续续实盘操作了一两年，收益理所当然是负的</p>\n<p>其实收益正负也倒还好，关键是感觉水平完全没提升，不像自己写代码或者学技术，明显的知道路线规划和学到什么程度了可以做出什么样的东西</p>\n<p>所以想问问大家，如果想炒股有这种掌控感、自信，应该是怎么一个学习路线呢</p>\n","last_modified":1668134959,"replies":14,"id":894399},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20